Value: Triangle Energy (Global) Limited engages in the exploration and production of oil and gas properties in Australia. It holds a 78.75% interest in Cliff Head Oil Field with a production license covering 72 square kilometers and the oil field covering 6 square kilometers, located in Perth Basin, Western Australia. The company also holds a 45% interest in the Xanadu-1 oil field and a 100% interest in the Mt Horner Production licence located in the Perth Basin, as well as an 100% operating interest in the Reids Dome production licence in Queensland. Triangle Energy (Global) Limited is headquartered in West Perth, Australia.
